<Base
  title="Progress in Medicine"
  description="A 6-week summer career exploration program for high school students interested in medicine, biotech, health &amp; longevity."
>
  <MediaHero
    src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Teens-with-surgery-robot-v3.png"
    width={1824}
    height={656}
  />
  <section class="newsletter">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="col-6-sm">
          <div class="text" set:html={`2026 program is filled &amp; applications are closed.`} />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6-sm" set:html={`<a href="https://rootsofprogress.org/subscribe/"><u>Sign up to for the RPI newsletter</u> </a>&amp; receive info about the 2027 program`} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="text" data-view>
    <Fragment set:html={`<div class="container"> <div class="grid"> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="max t--fadedown" ><h2>Progress in Medicine 2026</h2><p><b>A Summer Career Exploration Program for High School Students</b></p></div> </div> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250" ><p><i>People today live longer, healthier, and less painful lives than ever before. Why? Who made those changes possible? Can we keep this going? And could you play a part?</i></p> <p>Discover careers in medicine, biology, and related fields while developing practical tools and strategies for building a meaningful life and career— learning how to find mentors, identify your values, and build a career you love that drives the world forward.</p></div> </div> </div> </div>`} />
  </section>
  <section class="text" data-view style="background:#EDEADE">
    <Fragment set:html={`<div class="container"> <div class="grid"> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="max t--fadedown" ><h2>Explore careers in medicine, biotech, health policy &amp; longevity</h2></div> </div> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250" ><p><b>5 weeks live online</b>,&nbsp;2 hours a day (1-3 pm PT/4-6 pm ET), 4 days/week, Monday - Thursday<br>June 15-July 10 &amp; July 20-24</p><p><b>4 days in person</b>&nbsp;in-residency program at Stanford University in Palo Alto, CA with small-group tours to labs and bio-tech companies in the Bay Area<br>July 15-19</p><p>Program cost is $2,000; scholarships are available.&nbsp;</p></div> </div> </div> <div class="grid hspace-between-xs"> <div class="block-f"> <div class="icon" ><img width="500" height="500" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/PiM-Stethoscope.svg" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="attachment-medium size-medium"></div> <div class="text" ><b>Explore the fields of medicine, health, and biotechnology.</b>&nbsp;Dive into case studies in the history of medicine and gain context for the problems you can help solve today.&nbsp;</div> </div> <div class="block-f"> <div class="icon" ><img width="500" height="500" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Community.svg" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="attachment-medium size-medium"></div> <div class="text" ><b>Meet real world expert mentors.</b>&nbsp;Learn from senior experts. Find role models and mentors among young professionals.</div> </div> <div class="block-f"> <div class="icon" ><img width="500" height="500" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Mentors.svg" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="attachment-medium size-medium"></div> <div class="text" ><b>Find your community</b>&nbsp;in a cohort of ambitious high school students from all over the country who share your interested in medicine &amp; related fields.&nbsp;</div> </div> <div class="block-f"> <div class="icon" ><img width="500" height="500" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/College.svg" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="attachment-medium size-medium"></div> <div class="text" ><b>Prepare for college and scholarship or grant&nbsp; applications</b>.&nbsp;Become clearer on your goals and practice writing a common app suitable essay.</div> </div> </div> </div>`} />
  </section>
  <section class="newsletter">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="col-6-sm">
          <div class="text" set:html={`2026 program is filled &amp; applications are closed.`} />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6-sm" set:html={`<u>Sign up to for the RPI newsletter</u>&nbsp;&amp; receive info about the 2027 program`} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <ExpertGrid
    heading="Expert advisors"
    description={`<p>Leaders and experts who can share decades of experience and provide insight on who succeeds in their fields, how, and why. Many have interesting stories to tell and twists and turns in their careers that will broaden your perspective on the many ways you can impact human health.</p><p><b>Click on "Learn more"</b> to read about their unique missions and the paths they took to get there.</p>`}
    experts={experts}
  />
  <section class="newsletter">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="col-6-sm">
          <div class="text" set:html={`2026 program is filled &amp; applications are closed.`} />
        </div>
        <div class="col-6-sm" set:html={`<u><a href="https://rootsofprogress.org/subscribe/">Sign up to for the RPI newsletter</a>&nbsp;</u>&amp; receive info about the 2027 program`} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <AgendaSection
    heading="Weekly programming and sessions"
    description={`<div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250" ><p>The Zoom sessions will be highly interactive, which is why live attendance is critical. You will participate in break-out sessions, create “chat floods” with comments in Zoom, ask expert guests questions you have, and give each other feedback and support.&nbsp;</p><p>Note: the final week (July 20-24) will be five days dedicated to writing your end-of-program essay, using the 10-hour essay method.&nbsp;</p>`}
    imageSrc="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/PiM-WeeklyProgramming.svg"
    imageWidth={1315}
    imageHeight={556}
  />
  <AgendaSection
    heading="The Bay Area &amp; Stanford College Experience&nbsp;"
    description={`<div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250" ><p>During your time in the Bay Area, you will live in the Stanford dorms (double occupancy)</p><p><i>Tentative schedule; details may change as we confirm company tours and labs</i></p>`}
    imageSrc="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/PiM-BayArea-StandfordCollegeExperience-v2.svg"
    imageWidth={1315}
    imageHeight={548}
  />
  <section class="text" data-view style="background:#EDEADE">
    <Fragment set:html={`<div class="container"> <div class="grid"> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="max t--fadedown" ><h2><i>Organizational Partners</i></h2><p><i>During the in-person experience in the Bay Area, students will be able to choose from a range of labs, university departments, and companies to tour. Here are a handful of confirmed partners; we will add to that list by the time the program starts in summer.&nbsp;</i></p></div> </div> <div class="col-12-sm"> <div class="testimonials"> <div class="splide" role="group" aria-label="Testimonials" data-splide="{ &quot;type&quot;: &quot;loop&quot;, &quot;speed&quot;: 1000, &quot;perPage&quot;: 1, &quot;perMove&quot;: 1, &quot;gap&quot;: 40, &quot;rewind&quot; : true, &quot;autoplay&quot;: true, &quot;interval&quot;: 3000, &quot;arrows&quot;: true, &quot;pagination&quot;: false, &quot;breakpoints&quot;: { &quot;768&quot; : { &quot;perPage&quot;: 1 } } }"> <div class="splide__track"> <div class="splide__list" data-count="4"><div class="splide__slide" > <div class="block-t"> <div class="photo" ><img width="688" height="688" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM.png" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM.png 688w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-300x300.png 300w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-150x150.png 150w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-120x120.png 120w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px" class="attachment-large size-large"></div> <div class="text" ><p>The Snyder Lab at Stanford does research to better understand the connection between genes, cells, and diseases.&nbsp;</p><p>We will attend a talk by lab leaders and tour some of the lab facilities.</p></div> <div class="author" ><mark><a href="https://med.stanford.edu/content/sm/snyderlab.html/" target="_blank" tabindex="-1">Snyder Lab</a></mark></div> </div> </div><div class="splide__slide" > <div class="block-t"> <div class="photo" ><img width="688" height="688" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM.png" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM.png 688w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-300x300.png 300w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-150x150.png 150w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-11.51.35-AM-120x120.png 120w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px" class="attachment-large size-large"></div> <div class="text" ><p>The Goodman Surgical Education Center uses surgical simulation to equip surgeons, surgical residents, and medical students with the skills they need to provide state-of-the-art care and research the future of surgery.&nbsp;</p><p>Students will have the opportunity to tour the center, meet fellows, and practice hands-on technical skills on cutting edge surgical simulators.</p></div> <div class="author" ><mark><a href="https://med.stanford.edu/goodmancenter/aboutus.html" target="_blank">Goodman Surgical Education Center</a></mark></div> </div> </div><div class="splide__slide" > <div class="block-t"> <div class="photo" ><img width="1013" height="685" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/LOGO_PICT_MultiplyLabs_2022_candidate_version-1.svg" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="attachment-large size-large"></div> <div class="text" ><p>Multiply Labs is building the robotic future of biomanufacturing, tackling the biggest challenges in helping the most advanced therapies reach patients at scale.</p><p>Tour the lab to see the robots in action, and meet some of the people who make it happen.</p></div> <div class="author" ><mark><a href="https://multiplylabs.com/" target="_blank" tabindex="-1">Multiply Labs</a></mark></div> </div> </div><div class="splide__slide" > <div class="block-t"> <div class="photo" ><img width="616" height="616" src="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screenshot-2025-12-12-at-3.14.58-PM.png" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screenshot-2025-12-12-at-3.14.58-PM.png 616w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screenshot-2025-12-12-at-3.14.58-PM-300x300.png 300w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screenshot-2025-12-12-at-3.14.58-PM-150x150.png 150w, https://rootsofprogress.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Screenshot-2025-12-12-at-3.14.58-PM-120x120.png 120w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px" class="attachment-large size-large"></div> <div class="text" ><p>The Stanford Institute for Economic Policy Research (SIEPR) uses evidence to shift policy in a positive direction. Supporting nonpartisan economic policy research. Convening leaders from academia and business. Inspiring the next generation of economic experts.<br><br>Meet with Neale Mahoney, SIEPR' s Director who worked on health policy in the Obama and Biden administration, for an engaging Q&amp;A on research and insights on healthcare markets and the economics of health in the US and beyond.</p></div> <div class="author" ><mark><a href="https://siepr.stanford.edu/" target="_blank" tabindex="-1">SIEPR</a></mark></div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>`} />
  </section>
  <VideoSection
    headline="Program overview video"
    embedUrl="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/fnVzcbLWFZE?si=B--WTQHomNeRJOdB"
    videoTitle="Meet your instructor"
    videoLink="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fnVzcbLWFZE"
    excerpt={`Laura Mazer shares why she's excited about this program. She's developed a curriculum that will leave you in awe of the progress we've made in medicine, and inspired to contribute to the future in biotech, health, and medicine.<p><br></p><p>Watch this 5-minute video to get a better feel for what you'll learn during the program.</p>`}
    tags={[]}
    background="#fff"
  />
