div class="col-6-md" style="background:#FFFCF2"> <div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250"> <div class="acc" data-count="3"><div class="row" > <div class="q"><span >Step 1: Complete the written online application (1-2 hours)</span></div> <div class="a"> <div class="inside" ><p>A <a href="https://rootsofprogress.typeform.com/progresscareers">written application i</a>ncluding short answer questions and background information.&nbsp; <br><br>If you need a scholarship, there’s an optional section in the application where you can tell us more about your situation and financial needs.</p><p>Expected time needed to complete: 1-2 hours</p><p><br></p></div> </div> </div><div class="row" > <div class="q"><span >Step 2: Join a 45-min Zoom interview</span></div> <div class="a"> <div class="inside" ><p>We’ll invite a select number of applicants to Zoom calls with a Roots of Progress Institute staff member. The goal here is to get to know you, and to ensure that every participant is comfortable interacting via Zoom, which will be a key part of the summer program.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p></div> </div> </div><div class="row" > <div class="q"><span >Step 3: Commit to the program expectations &amp; pay program fees (30 min)</span></div> <div class="a"> <div class="inside" ><p>The last step is to verify your availability to attend the Zoom sessions and the in-person experience. We expect this program, as with our others, to have more applicants than our available spaces. Please enroll only if you can commit to fully participate in all parts of the program. You’ll also need to pay the program fee (or accept a scholarship, if offered), and send a transcript pdf to confirm the GPA you self-reported in the written application.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p></div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div> </div> </div>`} />
  </section>
  <section class="text" data-view>
    <Fragment set:html={`<div class="container"> <div class="grid"> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="max t--fadedown" ><h2>2027 Program timeline</h2></div> </div> <div class="col-6-md"> <div class="text t--fadedown t--delay_250" ><p><b>Progress in Medicine 2027 expected application timeline</b></p><p>We expect to announce the 2027 sometime in November - December 2026. Priority applications will be due sometime in early February; if spots remain we'll continue to accept applications through March.&nbsp;</p><p>We will review applications starting in February 2027, and expect to make offers in late March 2027. Admitted students must confirm enrollment within 14 days of offer. Applicants who apply before the February priority deadline receive first consideration for limited financial aid.</p></div> </div> </div> </div>`} />
  </section>
